There's campaign where perform tasks to advance through levels, or where you can just pick what type of game you play (avoid objects, collect spheres, kill bad guys, etc).  You can watch replays of your top games with a user controlled camera which is neat.  I usually go for complex RPGs and mmorpgs, but my hands literally hurt from playing this for hours.
